Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.05,Nápis,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(552,310)\b1}p\Nř\Ná\Nt\Ne\Nl\Ns\Nt\Nv\Ní{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Už se nudím. Pojďme to zklidit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrý nápad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.87,KopieNápis,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs120\frz270\pos(495,235)}_____
